  <brief_title>Bioavailability of the Fixed Combination of Amodiaquine and Artesunate Under Fed &amp; Fasted Conditions</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Open-Label, Cross-Over Study, to Compare the Bioavailability of the Fixed Combination of Amodiaquine and Artesunate (COARSUCAM™) After Single Oral Administration Under Fed and Fasted Conditions in Healthy Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
