    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Sanofi</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      -  Primary Objective: to evaluate the interaction with food after a single oral dose of a
           fixed combination of amodiaquine (AQ) and artesunate (AS) (COARSUCAM™) in healthy male
           subjects

        -  Secondary Objective: to assess the clinical and biological safety and tolerability of
           Coarsucam™
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
